description:
When a group of teens accidentally unleashes the power of evil upon the world, they must band together and put it back where it belongs... Will they succeed, or will this ancient magic wind up getting the better of them on this Halloween night?
Sonic Underground The Movie: Halloween Heroes (2023) | Final Trailer coming October 20th!
